TY  - JOUR
TI  - Revealed Preference--A Structural Analysis
AU  - Anthony Y. C. Koo
AB  - [This paper is designed to make revealed preference an operational tool of research on utility theory. The preference relations are shown in Boolean matrices and digraphs to facilitate the processing of a large quantity of empirical data and to classify different types and degrees of consumer rationality.]
